data.description: Southern Charm at it's finest! This fantastic home is located in North Canton inside the quiet, beautiful community of Silver Creek. You will immediately fall in love with the wrap around porch and 3rd car detached garage! Once inside enjoy true hardwood floors and high ceilings! Off the entry are home office/flex space and a formal dining room. Continuing back you will find a large family room and the the eat in kitchen complete with island and tons of cabinet space. Upstairs you and your family can unwind in the 4 large bedrooms! The Owner's suite is spacious and luxurious with en suite complete with 2 separate vanities, soaking tub, and separate shower. The secondary bathroom is in the hallway and provides tons of space! The fun continues downstairs where you will find the finished basement complete with full bathroom and great room space that can easily be used for a recreational area or 5th bedroom. The detached garage boasts additional storage/entertainment space with a huge loft above the garage! The back deck and back patio are huge and the perfect for all of your outdoor entertainment as they overlook the private backyard. Call today for your private showing!
